name: Low Fidelity Components
description:
Want to bring together a design during a coffee break? Just use the low-fi components from this file get to it. This way you get to spend the time on design thinking rather than creating some basic shapes or components.


You can find,

  1. Components - Ready to use base components
  2. Patterns - Ready to use structured pages


Got a requirement? Buzz me and I will be more than happy to add them in the library.
